snippet.title: The Adventures of Jerry Mouse: The Rescue of Nibbles - NES Hack
snippet.description:
In this video, I play through all the levels (with rewind on RetroArch) to show you all the levels in this Tom & Jerry themed Super Mario Bros. 1 hack.

You can check out the hack here: https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/3993/

Hack developed by Green Jerry
